The display will be in the center because, after using flex, if we use the align-items center,
then the items will be aligned at the center. This is because of the div, and inside the div there are three motives to do so.
To arrange such kinds of elements, we use align-items center. If we use flex-direction column, the items will be in the column. 
If we use flex-direction row, then the items will be arranged in the row. 



